      "message": "from my perspective both the `Severity` and `Direction` field here duplicate information from the `Name` field.\n\nI don\u0027t get why we need to duplicate things here.\n\nCan we not generate both `Direction` and `Severity` automatically from `Name` and delete both `Severity` and `Direction` from the schema and all configs?\n\nOr alternatively generate `Name` from `Severity` and `Direction` ?\n\nThat way we do not have any magic numbers in the EM config and the API remains stable. Let me know if i missed anything.\n\n\nOverall not in favor of further bloating the Threshold configuration.",
